      "rationale": "Use error factor was not formally assessed for this submission cycle. An informal peer review of model inputs was conducted internally, but no documented independent verification of analyst setup decisions against a pre-approved simulation plan was completed. Given modelRiskLevel 3, this gap materially weakens the overall credibility of the package."
