      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity applied to titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) with parameters from ASTM E8 tensile coupon testing. Augmented Lagrangian contact at screw-rod interface. Sensitivity analysis confirmed model form contributes less than 5% variance to stiffness QoI."
