      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and UTS (950 MPa) sourced from lot-specific coupon testing of the same material batch used in bench specimens. Geometric dimensions measured via CMM on three representative screws; nominal CAD dimensions within 0.02 mm of measured values."
