      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the primary ASTM F1717 endpoints and directly correspond to clinical construct performance under physiological compression-bending loads. These QoIs are accepted by FDA as relevant surrogates for in vivo pedicle screw construct integrity."
